Samuel Ondieki, alias Sammy Boy, has released party song 'Zoza' ahead of Valentine's day. Sammy Boy told Word Is he wanted to give his fans a new side of him after the many times he has trended online. "I will be doing more music in future and also work with big artistes. It's a new journey and I know it's going to work," he said. Sammy is popularly known for making a living through forex trading. He was listed among the top 100 young traders and feted for it in Kigali. Sammy has been in the news lately for leaked images, and he repeatedly defended his past working as a cam model. He said he started making money through online research when he was a student at USIU. He gradually started to make a few pennies, which helped him support himself in Nairobi.